The evidence with the title 'Allan Fung - Wikipedia ' says Allan Wai-Ket Fung (born february 25, 1970) is an American attorney and politician who has been mayor of Cranston , Rhode Island since 2009. He was the Republican nominee for governor of Rhode Island in the 2014 election and 2018 election . Elected mayor in 2008, Fung became the first mayor of Chinese ancestry in  ... . His proposed budget for Cranston in 2018 did not include a tax increase . 
